Ben Sherman REED v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 5550. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Jan. 4, 1957. Anthis & Gotcher, Muskogee, Okl., and Willard Gotcher, McAlester, Okl., for appellant. Frank D. McSherry, U. S. Atty., Muskogee, Okl., for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and HUXMAN and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of appellant.
